{{New unreviewed article|source=ArticleWizard|date=April 2011}}

[[Image:Nawa-jinja_Rōmon.jpg|thumb|right|300px|Nawa Jinja in [[Daisen, Tottori|Daisen]]]]

{{nihongo|'''Nawa Jinja'''|名和神社}} is a [[Shinto shrine]] in [[Daisen, Tottori|Daisen]], [[Tottori Prefecture]], [[Japan]]. It is celebrated for its [[cherry blossoms]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://yokoso.pref.tottori.jp/dd.aspx?menuid=1873 |title=Nawa Jinja |publisher=[[Tottori Prefecture]] |accessdate=23 April 2011}}</ref>

==See also==
{{Commonscategory|Nawa-jinja}}
* [[Mount Daisen]]
* [[Ōgamiyama Jinja]]

